1282
01:22:23.421 --> 01:22:25.354
in New Haven. Connecticut.

1283
01:22:25.388 --> 01:22:29.875
San Francisco was all everyone
talked about.

1284
01:22:29.910 --> 01:22:35.502
California officials continued
to deny that the plague existed.

1285
01:22:35.536 --> 01:22:39.437
in direct contradiction to the
MHS and national papers.

1286
01:22:42.371 --> 01:22:48.480
Other state boards of
health started issuing censure votes

1287
01:22:48.515 --> 01:22:53.244
