1291
01:23:08.949 --> 01:23:10.606
Well. this was serious.

1292
01:23:10.640 --> 01:23:15.059
San Francisco did not want
to risk such a loss of power.

1293
01:23:16.750 --> 01:23:18.510
At this point.

1294
01:23:18.545 --> 01:23:20.996
the denial of plague became costly.

1295
01:23:23.446 --> 01:23:26.070
California had run out of options.

1296
01:23:26.104 --> 01:23:30.039
It was time to face it. and
clean it out. and stamp it out.

1297
01:23:32.593 --> 01:23:35.079
The responsibility
of controlling the plague

1298
01:23:35.113 --> 01:23:37.012
rested squarely on Blue's shoulders.

1299
01:23:39.497 --> 01:23:40.912
Blue's boxing

