1345
01:26:25.870 --> 01:26:29.494
"People should not be frightened.

1346
01:26:29.529 --> 01:26:32.117
"These physicians are very kind
and gentle.

1347
01:26:32.152 --> 01:26:37.226
Their main emphasis is to go
after the rats."

1348
01:26:39.124 --> 01:26:41.265
"Chung Sai Yat Po Daily."

1349
01:26:45.061 --> 01:26:48.996
The state was assigned to hire inspectors.

1350
01:26:49.031 --> 01:26:50.791
The city would lay traps

