1385
01:29:35.059 --> 01:29:38.303
an extremely dangerous earthquake.

1386
01:29:38.338 --> 01:29:40.823
particularly in a city of unreinforced

1387
01:29:40.858 --> 01:29:42.791
brick and mortar buildings
