1388
01:29:48.072 --> 01:29:51.938
Buildings were pancaked. floors collapsed.

1389
01:29:53.664 --> 01:29:55.148
The city was ablaze.

1390
01:29:55.182 --> 01:29:58.910
water mains were broken.

1391
01:29:58.945 --> 01:30:03.121
So. the water reservoirs were
not available to fight fires.

1392
01:30:03.156 --> 01:30:07.022
In a desperate attempt to stop
the advancing flames.

1393
01:30:07.056 --> 01:30:11.060
the city resorted to setting
strategic charges

1394
01:30:11.095 --> 01:30:13.787
to keep the fire from jumping.

1395
01:30:15.410 --> 01:30:16.790
That helped a little bit.

1396
01:30:16.825 --> 01:30:21.830
but some ne'er-do-wells started
dynamiting Chinatown

1397
01:30:21.864 --> 01:30:23.348
indiscriminately.

1398
01:30:23.383 --> 01:30:25.212
destroying buildings even further.

1399
01:30:28.802 --> 01:30:32.979
More than 80%
of San Francisco was destroyed.

1400
01:30:33.013 --> 01:30:36.569
including virtually all of Chinatown.

1401
01:30:40.055 --> 01:30:44.024
There were 3.000 people killed outright.

1402
01:30:44.059 --> 01:30:47.131
Nearly a quarter million injured.

1403
01:30:47.165 --> 01:30:49.547
hundreds of thousands homeless.

1404
01:30:52.792 --> 01:30:55.484
And you had refugees who suddenly

1405
01:30:55.519 --> 01:30:58.142
have to live in places like
Golden Gate Park

1406
01:30:58.176 --> 01:31:00.627
or other makeshift camps.

1407
01:31:03.319 --> 01:31:05.563
People were living out of tents.

1408
01:31:05.598 --> 01:31:08.359
People were living in a village
of earthquake cottages

1409
01:31:08.393 --> 01:31:10.982
built by the Red Cross.

1410
01:31:14.365 --> 01:31:18.611
The Army and Red Cross
handed out crackers and canned milk.

1411
01:31:18.645 --> 01:31:21.752
But when word spread that no such aid

1412
01:31:21.786 --> 01:31:24.030
would be given to the Chinese.

1413
01:31:24.064 --> 01:31:27.654
the community once again turned
to its own devices.

1414
01:31:32.107 --> 01:31:34.143
Four years earlier.

1415
01:31:34.178 --> 01:31:38.527
merchant Lew Hing had moved away
from San Francisco.

1416
01:31:38.562 --> 01:31:43.912
Lew Hing decided
to open a cannery in Oakland.

1417
01:31:43.946 --> 01:31:45.845
away from San Francisco.

1418
01:31:48.572 --> 01:31:53.266
Having been tired of being
harassed by the white media.

1419
01:31:53.300 --> 01:31:57.477
having had to compete against
the white canneries

1420
01:31:57.512 --> 01:31:59.548
that had formed a cartel

1421
01:31:59.583 --> 01:32:01.930
to try and drive all the
independent canneries

1422
01:32:01.964 --> 01:32:05.140
out of business.

1423
01:32:05.174 --> 01:32:06.866
and particularly targeted Lew Hing

1424
01:32:06.900 --> 01:32:09.903
because he had become such a
force in the cannery business.

1425
01:32:14.149 --> 01:32:17.566
When the earthquake hit on April 18.

1426
01:32:17.601 --> 01:32:19.982
the Chinese in San Francisco.
they were refused

1427
01:32:20.017 --> 01:32:27.507
by the white relief agencies
and had no place to go.

1428
01:32:27.542 --> 01:32:30.337
And so many of the Chinese came
to a very small

1429
01:32:30.372 --> 01:32:33.306
Chinese settlement in Oakland

1430
01:32:33.340 --> 01:32:37.344
where my great-grandfather.
who had some vacant areas

1431
01:32:37.379 --> 01:32:38.932
around his cannery.

1432
01:32:38.967 --> 01:32:44.110
he then hired people to cook.

1433
01:32:44.144 --> 01:32:48.701
and was able to feed thousands
of the Chinese who came over.

1434
01:32:56.260 --> 01:32:59.815
San Francisco
was staggering to regain its footing

1435
01:32:59.850 --> 01:33:02.197
amidst the devastation.

1436
01:33:03.647 --> 01:33:05.372
And the fallout continued to escalate.

1437
01:33:08.168 --> 01:33:11.551
You had instant problems with sanitation.

1438
01:33:11.586 --> 01:33:13.208
If you didn't die from the earthquake.

1439
01:33:13.242 --> 01:33:14.899
or die from the fire.

1440
01:33:14.934 --> 01:33:16.798
you might die from diphtheria or smallpox

1441
01:33:16.832 --> 01:33:18.144
or all these other diseases

1442
01:33:18.178 --> 01:33:21.078
that could rear their head very quickly.

1443
01:33:21.112 --> 01:33:23.045
With the sewer pipes ruptured.

1444
01:33:23.080 --> 01:33:25.738
rats. including plague-infected ones.

1445
01:33:25.772 --> 01:33:28.223
were released into the city to feast

1446
01:33:28.257 --> 01:33:31.329
on the uncollected refuse.
