On this otherwise
unassuming residential street

1455
01:34:01.428 --> 01:34:05.640
in a Victorian house. Dr. Blue
set up his new headquarters.

1456
01:34:05.674 --> 01:34:09.022
and from there. he ran his command center.

1457
01:34:11.646 --> 01:34:13.337
The problem they find very quickly

1458
01:34:13.371 --> 01:34:16.685
is that plague is no longer
a Chinatown problem.

1459
01:34:16.720 --> 01:34:18.687
it's a San Francisco problem.

1460
01:34:20.275 --> 01:34:22.587
In stark contrast to the early days.

1461
01:34:22.622 --> 01:34:26.591
there was now only one Chinese casualty:

1462
01:34:26.626 --> 01:34:29.698
the president of
the Chinese Six Companies.

1463
01:34:29.733 --> 01:34:32.494
And that's when Blue starts hearing

1464
