1474
01:35:04.802 --> 01:35:07.529
Blue set up a special workplace

1475
01:35:07.563 --> 01:35:10.118
dedicated to the grisly task at hand.

1476
01:35:11.567 --> 01:35:12.948
In back of

1477
01:35:12.983 --> 01:35:15.744
the federal headquarters was an
annex to the building

1478
01:35:15.779 --> 01:35:16.987
that became known as the Rattery.

1479
01:35:18.782 --> 01:35:21.577
And the Rattery was essentially
a coroner's lab.

1480
01:35:21.612 --> 01:35:24.097
a forensic lab. just for rats.

1481
01:35:26.582 --> 01:35:30.241
That's where all
the rat carcasses were brought.

1482
01:35:30.276 --> 01:35:34.314
