They wanted to find out where
the rats originated

1494
01:36:11.800 --> 01:36:14.838
and where they traveled.

1495
01:36:14.872 --> 01:36:16.598
So. they devised a program

1496
01:36:16.632 --> 01:36:19.946
that came to be nicknamed
the rainbow rats.

1497
01:36:19.981 --> 01:36:23.018
and they got a group of healthy.
active rats

1498
01:36:23.053 --> 01:36:25.434
and dyed them red. green. or blue.

1499
01:36:25.469 --> 01:36:27.264
depending upon what district
they were from.

1500
01:36:27.298 --> 01:36:28.575
and turned them loose.

1501
01:36:28.610 --> 01:36:31.578
Then they would try to catch
them at the other end

1502
01:36:31.613 --> 01:36:35.859
and find out how they were spreading.

1503
01:36:35.893 --> 01:36:37.515
And. of course.

1504
